Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the wolvified Weslie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,nearly ate Wolffy and his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,However, at the same time, he foiled Werewolf’s plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, he recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for sending me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the least we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,when I’ll get to see you guys again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you’ll see us once you return to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe travels!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can finally go home and rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why’s he sneaking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you guys sent Weslie home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you holding, Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s with the secretiveness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s… It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just stuff that Wolnie wanted me to buy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolnie uses a shaver, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a shaver on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but in reality, it’s a…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,a women’s cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how I look at it, it looks like a shaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolnie’s calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolnie, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t be home for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,These slippers are a bit big, aren’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Wolnie’s feet this big?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,These…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,These are for killing cockroaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing cockroaches?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you’d need!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s up, Doudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Something’s gone wrong in the timespaces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s head to the Hub right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll bring my stuff home first and catch up to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The past Weslie is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that Werewolf took the past Weslie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find him as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, what…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,what’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What… What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I’m
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,turning transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be because the past Weslie
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is in a critical condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Weslie, come to Rainbow for medical attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll have to rescue the past Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure we’ll find my past self.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonie, take Weslie back to Goats’ Village for now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and see if Slowy has any other solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry. You’ll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let time move a little faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My undersea world will be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie’s turning even more transparent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The present Weslie can only be saved
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,if the past Weslie is rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll see if there’s anything else we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can’t we find him anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve already looked in all the places that we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Werewolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he coming to laugh at us or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on the airplanes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve searched every place
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,except for Werewolf’s airplane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Werewolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught up to me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t let them—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Weslie go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Weslie go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll have to catch me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Werewolf jammed his airplane’s signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie must be in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Weslie
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Tibbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m okay. Let’s get Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie isn’t here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you hidden Weslie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What “Weslie?”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know what you’re talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn’t take Weslie, what were you running for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Mr. Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be worried about you guys capturing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don’t tell me right now, I’ll—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1070)}Let’s head back to Goats’ Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn’t have much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don’t go now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you might not even get to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t fall asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s with all the sad faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you’ve already done your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1070)}You’ll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there. I know it’ll be okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so don’t cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls look prettier when they smile, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,no more slacking off from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky, keep an eye on him for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve grown up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No more of that capriciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to find Werewolf
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and force him to tell me where the past Weslie is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault for being impulsive, smashing the Gem,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and causing all of this trouble in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I’m out of chances to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s up to you to lead everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and do the next right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonie, keep an eye on them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and don’t let them mess around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Work hard to find the anachronists
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and save the world on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If we’re going, we’re going together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t leave behind any person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have we known each other, Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For around five thousand episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that many?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We met when goats and wolves were sworn enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and we’ve still been through so much together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, we managed to become friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,yet now, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Our time as friends may not have been long,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m very glad to have known you, Wolffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve… I’ve failed your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t look after you well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Mr. Slowy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for taking my parents’ place
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of these years
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and raising me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If, someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,my parents return,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,please give this bell to them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:13:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them that I’m very proud
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to be their son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re so smart, Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you think of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll take care of you from now on, Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s play soccer after homework, Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do now, Weslie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we’re friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
